  It is not until someone points it out that you realise how often you use your hands; to type, read, cook, talk, the list goes on. Unfortunately, our hands carry and transfer germs and bacteria from one surface to another which can be detrimental to your health, especially during these uncertain times. Clere For Men brand manager Themba Ndlovu shares his top hygiene tips to help stop germs from spreading in our homes: Being in lockdown does not mean your selfcare should be too. Put these hygiene tips to good use by adding them to you daily routine.